URL <- "https://www.ebi.ac.uk/arrayexpress/files/E-GEOD-41268"
SDRF.file <- "E-GEOD-41268.sdrf.txt"
Data.file <- "E-GEOD-41268.raw.1.zip"
if (! file.exists(SDRF.file)){
  download.file(paste(URL,SDRF.file,sep="/"), SDRF.file)
}
if (! file.exists(Data.file)){
  download.file(paste(URL,Data.file,sep="/"), Data.file)
  unzip(Data.file)
}
